data.description: Welcome golf community enthusiasts! This is your chance to own a rare and stunning property in a desirable Palm Valley neighborhood.  Backing to Palm Valley Golf Club, a 27 hole championship course designed by Arthur Hill.  This executive estate offers an alluring lifestyle with direct golf course views from nearly every room in the home.  You'll love the spacious floorplan with five large bedrooms PLUS an office.  The home is immaculate with elegant high ceilings, crisp new paint and artful natural light.  An excellent home to entertain or simply enjoy the space all to yourself.  The patio deck provides a front-row seat to the beauty of the golf course. Expecting significant interest - request your private tour right away!
